            <div>
                <head>Comments</head>
                <p xml:id="CH2b1559-start">
                    <seg corresp="#CH2b1559_CHANT_005-1a.24" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-05-13T18:15:36.881+09:00">This point has long been obfuscated</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH2b1559_CHANT_005-1a.25" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-05-13T18:16:40.101+09:00">and no one has been willing to come to its rescue</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH2b1559_CHANT_005-1a.26" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-05-13T18:17:28.146+09:00">so this has caused the issue remain</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH2b1559_CHANT_005-1a.27" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-05-13T18:17:46.67+09:00">unclear terminologically and objectively.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH2b1559_CHANT_005-1a.29" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-05-13T18:23:22.686+09:00">Now when Heaven and earth combine theirPowers</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH2b1559_CHANT_005-1a.30" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-05-13T18:24:09.157+09:00">then the myriad kinds of creatures come to value their lives.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH2b1559_CHANT_005-1a.52" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-05-13T18:48:58.143+09:00">emotional harm</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH2b1559_CHANT_005-1a.54" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-05-13T18:51:23.372+09:00">On the basis of reality and of (available) designations</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH2b1559_CHANT_005-1a.55" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-05-13T18:52:31.268+09:00">things get their appellations.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH2b1559_CHANT_005-1a.58" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-05-13T21:57:53.931+09:00">史記貨殖列傳：「此其大較也殖索隱曰：「較音角，大較，猶大略也。」  Cai Zhongde：大致说来就是如此。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH2b1559_CHANT_005-1a.61" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-05-13T21:54:59.276+09:00">Cai Zhongde：note 14 "乐云"句：语出《论语♦收货》："礼云，礼云，玉帛云乎哉？乐云，乐云，钟鼓云乎哉？"此处虽只引"乐云"句，语意却兼含"礼云"句，故下文日"玉帛非礼敬之实: 又，这里引"乐云"句已改变《论语》原意，"乐"不是指音乐而是指快乐。 "兹"，此C "歌哭"句：原作"歌若非悲哀之主也:周校本以为"舞”当作"哭"，"悲哀"当作"哀乐"，今据改。“然乐云"七句承上文"哭谓之哀，歌谓之乐"而言，意为家哭不是哀乐的主体，歌哭不一定表现哀乐的感情。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH2b1559_CHANT_005-1a.59" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2025-05-13T22:03:38.929+09:00">Ji Liangkang：然而"攀呀，架呀，辘道是3g• 14 •^和鼓道些槃器喝? "哀呀，哀呀，辘道是Ig哭泣道槿琪象喝?⑯</seg>
                </p>
